707233f-a.title: Brooklyn: Ave. W - Ocean Parkway
707233f-a.text:
(1)
Ave. W., at the S.W. corner of Ocean Parkway, showing Ave. W.,under
construction. In 1923, this building Was used by the fire dept., and
was designated as Engine house No. 254. In 1929 it was converted and
used as a Police Department training station.
1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPIODUCED.
(2)
The samme, seen from Ocean Parkway.
March 1923.
Eugene L Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
